<p>Yep, another one of Dave&#39;s iMacs is having boot problems. It&#39;s mayhem! That&#39;s OK, he and John talk through possible resolution and also when&nbsp;<em>not</em>&nbsp;to assume you know the answer (hint: always!). Then it&#39;s on to maintaining your iTunes accounts, finding (and removing) any adware, and an unpublished solution to Yosemite&#39;s incrementing hostname issue. All this and more. Download today and enjoy!</p>
